title: Implement --agent CLI command for autonomous AI tasks
description:
Title: Implement --agent CLI command for autonomous AI tasks

Overview:
Add a new `--agent` flag to the CLI so that users can send a prompt to the OpenAI API directly from the command line and receive a structured JSON response. This feature enables CI/CD pipelines, GitHub Actions, and local automation scripts to leverage agentic-lib without writing custom code.

Requirements:
1. Import `Configuration` and `OpenAIApi` from the `openai` package in `src/lib/main.js`.
2. Implement `async function processAgent(args)` that:
